dc_description_s: This data group represents recreation and boat access locations for Polk County, Wisconsin in 2019 and includes the layers 'Polk_BoatAccess_2019' and 'Polk_Recreation_2019'. [Recreation: Location of Recreation Resources/Amenities in Polk County, Wisconsin.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.polkcountywi.gov/government/divisions_and_departments/environmental_services_division/land_information/gis_data_portal.php
